xfonts-wqy (1.0.0~rc1-7) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.

  [ Boyuan Yang ]
  * Bump debhelper compat to v13.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 4.5.1.
  * debian/rules: Remove custom dh_builddeb override.
  * debian/compat: Dropped, useless now.
  * debian/control: Remove Christian Perrier from uploaders list.
    (Closes: #927595)
  * debian/control: Replace explicit versioned dpkg pre-depends with
    ${misc:Pre-Depends}.
  * debian/control: Mark binary package as Multi-Arch: foreign.
  * debian/po: Convert all files to UTF-8 encoding.
  * debian/changelog: Remove trailing spaces.
  * debian/copyright: Use secure URI in Format field.
  * debian/postinst: Remove custom invocation to fc-cache. This is
    now automatically handled by fontconfig trigger.

  [ Hideki Yamane ]
  * debian/control
    - drop Suggests: xfs, removed from repository
      see http://bugs.debian.org/733958

